title: Middle Tennessee drops senior day contest to LA Tech - GoBlueRaiders.com
content: Middle Tennessee drops senior day contest to LA Tech  GoBlueRaiders.com
description: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. - Middle Tennessee (19-31, 6-15 C-USA) was unable to overcome another fast start by Louisiana Tech (35-17, 15-6 C-USA) as the Blue Raiders fell in theirÂ final game of the 2022 season at the Blue Raider Softball Field by a score of 6-3 on Sunday.
